description: D-day Counter simply can tell you how many weeks and days left until the date you say. Now it is simple and easy to know how long until the important date.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Date Counter how many weeks until December 25th
Alexa, ask Date Counter how many days until December 25th 2018
Alexa, ask Date Counter how long till December 25th
name: Date Counter
shortDescription: D-day Counter tells you how many weeks and days left until a specific date you mention.
